        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">1. Overview</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Job Club ("we," "us," "our") respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website and use our onboarding form, events system, and resource library.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          <strong>Mission:</strong> Turn students into career-ready AI professionals with a guided, automated onboarding experience.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section id="data-collected" class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">2. What Data We Collect</h2>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Onboarding Form (Mandatory)</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">When you complete our onboarding form, we collect:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-4">
          <li>Full name</li>
          <li>Email address (NJIT email preferred)</li>
          <li>Major/field of study</li>
          <li>Expected graduation year</li>
          <li>Career goal (consultant, startup founder, engineer, etc.)</li>
          <li>LinkedIn URL</li>
          <li>GitHub URL</li>
          <li>Personal portfolio website URL</li>
          <li>Calendly scheduling link</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Automatic Data Collection</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Device information:</strong> Device type, operating system, browser</li>
          <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> Pages viewed, time on site, clicks (with your consent)</li>
          <li><strong>Location data:</strong> General location (city/country level only, with consent)</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section id="how-we-use" class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">We use collected data to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Onboarding:</strong> Create your career profile in our CRM and track progress toward career readiness</li>
          <li><strong>Personalized Guidance:</strong> Send you customized career development checklists and resources matched to your goals</li>
          <li><strong>Community:</strong> Add you to our Discord mentoring community and post introductions</li>
          <li><strong>Events:</strong> Notify you of relevant workshops, office hours, and networking events</li>
          <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> Understand how students use the platform to improve career guidance quality</li>
          <li><strong>Communication:</strong> Send important updates about Job Club programs and opportunities</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

