        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Our Approach</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Job Club uses privacy-first analytics that <strong>do not set cookies or track personally identifiable information</strong>. 
          You must explicitly consent before any analytics tracking occurs.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">What You Control</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">You can manage your preferences by clicking the "Cookie Settings" button in the page footer:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
