      <section id="gdpr" class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">6. Your GDPR Rights</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Under GDPR, you have the right to:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-4">
          <li><strong>Access:</strong> Request a copy of your data</li>
          <li><strong>Rectification:</strong> Correct inaccurate data</li>
          <li><strong>Erasure:</strong> Request deletion of your data ("right to be forgotten")</li>
          <li><strong>Portability:</strong> Receive your data in a portable format</li>
          <li><strong>Opt-out:</strong> Withdraw consent for analytics and communications</li>
          <li><strong>Complaint:</strong> File a complaint with your data protection authority</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="text-gray-700">
          To exercise any of these rights, email us at <a href="mailto:jobclub@njit.edu" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">jobclub@njit.edu</a>
        </p>
      </section>

      <section id="data-retention" class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">7. Data Retention</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Onboarding Data:</strong> Retained for the duration of your time at NJIT plus 2 years</li>
          <li><strong>Analytics Data:</strong> Aggregated data retained for 90 days; individual sessions deleted after 30 days</li>
          <li><strong>Emails:</strong> Retained until you unsubscribe; opt-out link provided in every email</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="text-gray-700 mt-4">
          You can request deletion of your profile at any time. We will remove all data within 30 days.
        </p>
      </section>

